etically predicted value. This might be\nassociated with fluctuations which are neglected in the quasi-static\napproximation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2011 10:46:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2012 11:42:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-17"}
